<figureCitation box="[312,348,1172,1199]" captionStart="FIGURES 5" captionStartId="15.[151,264,1893,1918]" captionTargetBox="[157,1425,216,1869]" captionTargetId="figure@15.[151,1435,211,1874]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURES 5A–5I. Aedeagus of Agrilus mounted in DMHF. 5A–5C, 5E, 5I medial lobe (penis) exposed, 5D, 5F, 5H medial lobe (penis) in natural position. 5A, Agrilus acacivorus sp.nov.; 5B, A. albizivorus sp.nov.; 5C, A. babaulti Théry, 1930; 5D, A. monadikos sp.nov.; 5E, A. occultus sp.nov.; 5F, A. occultus sp.nov.; 5G, A. terraereginae Blackburn, 1892; 5H, A. viridicupreus Saunders, 1866; 5I, A. viridifrons Kerremans, 1893." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3268313/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="82">5D</figureCitation>
